review.reviewBody: Foods amazing but the pizza is SHOW STOPPER!! If you used to eat pizza in the mid 90s this is the place!! We have tried so many places in white rock and this is the best! So much cheese! Yummy
The Euro Veggie Pizza is the best vegetarian pizza I've had.  Enjoyed the Chicken Souvlaki very much.  We will definitely be back

Delicious as usual :-) :-) :-)  Mousaka SO creamy and yummy; Chicken Souvlaki yummy, ditto everything else :-)  Oh! Cheese Bread slices are HUGE! :-) 

First time trying the Tyropita ; VERY yummy! :-)  One of us hates feta cheese, but L-O-V-E-D the tyropita! (I know; weird: They really DID love it :-)  )
Pizzas were good and chicken souvlaki was yummy. Ribs were too salty.
Everything is always SO good. Hummus is made in house!!
